Social Studio Is Being Retired

Social Studio is being retired on November 18, 2024. When your existing contract ends or on November 18, 2024, whichever comes first, you can no longer access Social Studio. Your customer data will be deleted 90 days later in compliance with the Salesforce Marketing Cloud Security, Privacy, and Architecture (SPARC) documentation.

To switch to another approved Salesforce product, contact your account executive.

Where: This change applies to the Social Studio family of products: Social Studio, Command Center, Social Studio Mobile App, Social Studio Automate, and Social Customer Service (including the free Starter Pack offering).

How: We recommend that you retrieve your data 90 days before November 18, 2024 or the end of your contract, whichever is first. To retrieve your Social Studio data, see Social Studio Data Extracts.

Knowledge Article: Marketing Cloud Social Studio Retirement 
External Link: Salesforce Marketing Cloud Security, Privacy, and Architecture (SPARC)
title: Social Studio Retirement
